WEBVTT

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:02.960
what value does that life have left?

00:03:03.640 --> 00:03:05.496
That day in the truck,

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:09.696
all I could imagine
was that my dad was being tortured

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:12.680
and his body was
the vessel of that torture.

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:15.840
I've got to get him out of that body.

00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:19.440
I've got to get him out of that body;
I'm going to kill Dad.

00:03:20.600 --> 00:03:21.840
I call my sister.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:25.200
"Beth," she said.

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:30.936
"You don't want
to live the rest of your life